{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 192.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I guess they were called also the-- probably lower than the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were just completely undesirable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were called parasites.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were called parasites anyway all the time, but they were probably just even a step lower than us and they liquidated that camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "After spending I believe it was about five weeks, I believe it was-- could have been five weeks, less time-- time was really unimportant, it just went.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By the way, the barracks were just very long barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they had like a brick chimney-- chimney all the way through the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Supposedly, you put some wood and-- to get some heat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was never wood to burning anyway to heat the place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And supposedly, all the bricks would get warm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This is familiar to me because of the brick factory, which we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But there was never any heat in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And-- and the food that we had it was just-- they we just bring a little bit of water, supposedly warm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there were some-- I don't know, leaves, vegetables in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But we would get a small piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the first-- no, I'm jumping a little bit ahead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Then after about the four or five weeks, we were marched in to Auschwitz, which is an adjoining camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Birkenau was very close to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We marched into Auschwitz and we get-- and we had different barracks again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I do not remember my barrack number that I was in, but those were brick buildings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I guess they must have been either built for that purpose or they were built for-- for soldiers-- for soldiers barracks to be in there.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
